overview: The Jungle Soundclash Grand Final was held at Roller Express on 16th July 1994.  After the two semi finals on May 14th and June 18th the competition reached the final stage with Mickey Finn, Kenny Ken, DJ Rap and Devious Dee.  The referees and master of ceremonies on the night were the A team, Moose and Five-O.  It was down to you the Jungle Massive to decide who would become the champion and holder of the Lonsdale Jungle Soundclash Belt in 1994.
title: A Jungle Sound Clash "94"
